news.title: Pimpri Chinchwad: PCMC fines 421 construction sites for causing air pollution
news.para: Dedicated squads formed to initiate action against construction firms have issued notices for various violations at 421 sites in the last four days, and fines worth over Rs 33 lakh collectively have also been recovered from offenders.

news.title: Over 140 property registration offices in Maharashtra need relocation: Survey
news.para: Most of the offices identified for relocation are on the first floor, without lifts and are difficult to access, an official from the state registration department said.

news.title: Teething issues mar property data digitisation drive of Mangaluru civic body
news.para: Many property owners have raised concern about the need to re-submit copies of documents, such as building completion certificates, occupancy certificates, building licences, and khata or title deeds, to the MCC.
